    "The initial search identified 97 studies.",
    "To ensure thoroughness, we also examined the reference lists of the relevant studies.",
    "This, however, did not lead to additional relevant studies that met our inclusion criteria.",
    "The criteria for inclusion were English language fulllength publications that specifically evaluated the role of LLMs in breast cancer management.",
    "We excluded papers that addressed other general applications of LLMs in healthcare or oncology without a specific focus on breast cancer."
